• Paraphrase generator (multi-query) logic
• Decomposition module & orchestration code
• Re-ranker model + authority heuristics
• RAGAS evaluation harness + scripts for DeepEval/Grouse
• Human evaluation run & report (clinician ratings)
• Monitoring dashboard & alert rules